## Build & Run

- Java 17 toolchain; Forge 47.x; MC 1.20.1; mappings `official:1.20.1`
- Memory: `org.gradle.jvmargs=-Xmx10G` in [gradle.properties](mdc:gradle.properties)
- Mixins enabled via Sponge plugin and configured in [build.gradle](mdc:build.gradle); configs: [cataclysm.mixins.json](mdc:src/main/resources/cataclysm.mixins.json)
- Access transformer configured at [META-INF/accesstransformer.cfg](mdc:src/main/resources/META-INF/accesstransformer.cfg)

Common Gradle tasks (dev)
- Generate IDE runs: `genIntellijRuns` (or `genEclipseRuns`)
- Client/server/data runs are preconfigured in [build.gradle](mdc:build.gradle) with working dir `run/`

Publishing is configured to a local `mcmodsrepo`; jars are reobfuscated via `reobfJar`.

